sequenceDiagram
    participant DEV as Developer / IaC
    participant K8S as Kubernetes API
    participant ESO as External Secrets Operator
    participant VAULT as HashiCorp Vault /<br/>AWS Secrets Manager
    participant WORKLOAD as Application Pod

    DEV->>K8S: Apply ExternalSecret CR\n(references secret path)
    K8S->>ESO: ExternalSecret created
    ESO->>VAULT: Authenticate via IRSA / SPIFFE
    VAULT-->>ESO: Return secret value
    ESO->>K8S: Create / update Kubernetes Secret
    K8S->>WORKLOAD: Mount Secret as env var or volume
    Note over ESO,VAULT: Reconciliation loop (default: 1h)\nRotation is automatic
